metadata.name: The Descendant of Zack Taylor
metadata.description:
The Descendant of Zack Taylor is the alter ego of the PNW based artist and musician, The Rhetorician, who is a fan fiction character that is a fusion of Static Shock, Blankman, and The Famous Jett Jackson. 

The goggles on the outfit symbolize his part-time aquatic lifestyle.  After trying to find solace in the forest after his ex got pregnant, he ran into a captain who protected a magical hammer. The captain realized his blood relation and knew he was destined to protect the hammer!

Image taken on the set of the short film and music video "The Descendant of Zack Taylor: Episode 2".
